block variables
doctype html
html
  head
    title 'Bitcoin Cube'
    style
      include ../public/css/bootstrap.css
      include ../public/css/bootstrap.min.css
  body
    h3.h3='Bitcoin Cube'
    div.container.px-2.px-sm-3
      h2.lead OpenVPN
      |
      p
      |
      - var port_external = '443'
      - var url = 'https://' + ip_external + ':' + port_external + '/client.ovpn';
      |
      |
      p How to connect to the VPN
      p 1- Install the OpenVPN client on the device: Computer, mobile, Tablet ...
      p 2- Download the configuration file of this link 
        a(class='rounded bg-primary text-white px-2 py-1' href=url) client.ovpn
      p 3- Start the OpenVPN program
      p 4- In the OpenVPN program, add (+) -> Import Profile -> FILE, indicate the file that you have downloaded, the requested password is: <mark>password</mark>
      p
      p From the client device you have to have access to the web server and the port where you are listening to be able to download the file and to the port where you listen to the OpenVPN process (443)
      |
      p
      |
      a(class='rounded bg-primary text-white px-2 py-1' href="./") Home
    
